{"tid":1599333,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"嘲寄望英美打救　盧維思：豬都曉飛","createTime":"2019-09-28T02:21:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T02:35:11.000Z","uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2a00d4f253bc75498328755cf62aa198269b1133","tid":1599333,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T02:21:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1599648/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1599648%2F&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOjx%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=dd37c96f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1599648%2F&h=a933fd33\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1599648/</a><br />\n<br />\n嘲寄望英美打救 盧維思：豬都曉飛<br />\n2019-09-26 07:57 <br />\n<br />\n部分反修例抗爭者曾到英國和美國駐港總領事館請願，爭取兩國施加援手。已加入中國籍、曾於六月九日現身反修例遊行的前投資推廣署署長盧維思，周初投稿《南華早報》，認為若英美兩國會拯救香港的話，就如「豬都曉飛」。盧維思指，英國政府在八十年代已修訂政策，不容許香港在內的海外領土居民獲得英國居留權，繼而才誕生英國國民（海外）（BNO）護照，加上現時保守黨當政下的入境政策存在種族主義傾向，反移民情緒正是推動英國脫歐的元素之一，故他認為港人期望英國突然改變政策，給予港人居留權屬天方夜譚。<br />\n<br />\n他又指出，美國總統特朗普是藉反移民政綱當選，現時發聲關注香港只是為了打擊中國，直斥要求特朗普幫助港人的示威者「不要臉」。<br />\n<br />\n他呼籲部分港人拋棄外人會解決本港問題的「夢想」，強調香港永遠是中國的一部分，《基本法》才能給予港人所有現實能要的東西，希望港人腳踏實地，珍惜《基本法》，並與北京打好關係，香港未來才能得到保障。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190926/_2019092607593084010.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190926%2F_2019092607593084010.jpg&h=2eaae3a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e50a25efd9079ca022107983f9caeb8c156df45","tid":1599333,"uid":220701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T02:22:26.000Z","msg":"你老味我就係挑共產黨機<br />\n殺我全家囉"},{"pid":"26f07267f0b59a62c986875bf88dee424a146549","tid":1599333,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T02:23:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a4835d8dedc57dc5f43c11e9e3b51e3f79eec5a","tid":1599333,"uid":100697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T02:26:08.000Z","msg":"其實香港人係有腦咖 藍絲講D野全撚部都係一式一樣 錄音機黎<br />\n點會唔知英美兩國點對香港呀"},{"pid":"fa0ceda16fc6da9e034019eb1e1e9458521538ba","tid":1599333,"uid":324017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T02:30:22.000Z","msg":"先 search 下呢位前 &quot;Invest HK&quot; 的揸𨋢人所謂之政績，一塌糊塗，其所發表既言論，就知有何份量！"},{"pid":"4dd5147ad7712b71be5aa1e1484d51dd06b6aedc","tid":1599333,"uid":34189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T02:35:11.000Z","msg":"條友訓咗幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪講咗攬抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係要英美打救我哋,係要英美打鳩你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}